{"tid":54465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新田車禍】巴士車廂變形 上層頭排乘客浴血被困","createTime":"2016-12-25T14:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T18:54:48.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"080d18f856e8416a06ab5a3ff56187335e94909e","tid":54465,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:23:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161225&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56092485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161225%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56092485&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgH38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=8fc13318\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161225%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56092485&h=91ee2163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161225&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56092485</a><br />\n新田公路發生三車串燒意外，造成42人受傷。巴士乘客陳先生憶述，他與妻子攜同手抱嬰兒在東涌乘搭肇事巴士，擬在上水下車後再乘港鐵返回內地，當時他坐在下層中間位置，巴士行駛期間突然急煞，但收制不及猛撞前方貨櫃車車尾，他感覺兩車猛烈撞擊，雖然他與妻子急煞前已扶住扶手，但撞車一刻未能扶穩，結果前衝跌坐地上，夫妻分別扭傷頸部及擦傷手腳，幸當時抱緊幼子未有受傷。大約3分鐘後，巴士乘客再感受多一次由後方而來的小巴撞擊，引起全車乘客恐慌，要求車長開門，走至路肩暫避。他憶述事後有上層乘客及車長受困，他擔心車長情況一度上前慰問，幸對方能清晰對答事發公路位置，其後由消防及救護員救起送院。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qzup974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzup974.jpg&h=f2eb79e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f97a0b7da142f6da300e254099c4cc2de351026","tid":54465,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:23:56.000Z","msg":"架新龍運客車<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtaL4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtaL4.gif&h=610f0320&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtaL4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtaL4.gif&h=610f0320&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a25c56186e6465da2996482bb6614841b7f2c477","tid":54465,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:24:39.000Z